name: Loof Medley
chorusText:
Stand up (x2) for Jesus
Ye soldiers of the cross 
Lift high his royal banner 
It must not suffer loss, from victory unto victor, his army shall He lead
Till every foe is vanished
And Christ is Lord indeed
JESUS IS DIE NAAM VAN MY HEER EN VRIEND
Jesus is die Naam van my HeerenVriend,
Jesus is die Naam wat verlossingbied,
In syNaam is krag, oorwinning dag na dag,
HierdieNaamverdryfallevyandsmag
YOU ARE THE WORD AND THE MUSIC
You are the words and the music,
You are the song that I sing,
You are the melody,
You are the harmony,
Praise to Thy Name we’ll bring,
You are the mighty God,
You are the Lord above,
You are the King of all Kings,
Now I return to you
The song that You gave to me
You are the song that I sing
TOUCHING JESUS 
Touching Jesus is all that matters,
Then you life will never be the same,
There is only one way to touch Him,
Just believe when you call out His Name
